Class PairwiseAlignmentVisualizer

java.lang.Object
  cross.commands.fragments.AFragmentCommand
      maltcms.commands.fragments.visualization.PairwiseAlignmentVisualizer
All Implemented Interfaces:
IFragmentCommand, ICommand<TupleND<IFileFragment>,TupleND<IFileFragment>>, IWorkflowElement, IEventSource<IWorkflowResult>, IConfigurable, IXMLSerializable
public class PairwiseAlignmentVisualizer
extends AFragmentCommand

Plots a pairwise alignment, by displaying both time series' tics, connected by lines depicting the path obtained from alignment.

Author:
Nils.Hoffmann@cebitec.uni-bielefeld.de
